        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "heading_2",
      "heading_2": {
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "1. 概述"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "paragraph": {
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "本文档详细分析了 nanobot 系统中注入的提示词（Prompts），包括硬编码的提示词和通过文件注入的提示词。"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "heading_2",
      "heading_2": {
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "2. 通过文件注入的提示词"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "heading_3",
      "heading_3": {
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "2.1 核心引导文件（BOOTSTRAP_FILES）"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "paragraph": {
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "这些文件在系统启动时被加载，构成了代理的基本指令集："
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "code",
      "code": {
        "language": "markdown",
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "| 文件名 | 路径 | 作用 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| AGENTS.md | nanobot/templates/AGENTS.md | 代理指令，包含提醒和心跳任务的使用指南 |\n| SOUL.md | nanobot/templates/SOUL.md | 定义代理的人格、价值观和沟通风格 |\n| USER.md | nanobot/templates/USER.md | 用户配置文件，包含用户基本信息和偏好设置 |\n| TOOLS.md | nanobot/templates/TOOLS.md | 工具使用说明和约束 |"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "heading_3",
      "heading_3": {
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "2.2 代理模板文件"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "paragraph": {
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "这些文件定义了代理的身份和行为："
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "code",
      "code": {
        "language": "markdown",
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "| 文件名 | 路径 | 作用 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| identity.md | nanobot/templates/agent/identity.md | 核心身份信息，包含运行时环境和工作空间信息 |\n| platform_policy.md | nanobot/templates/agent/platform_policy.md | 平台特定的政策和指导 |\n| skills_section.md | nanobot/templates/agent/skills_section.md | 技能部分的模板 |\n| consolidator_archive.md | nanobot/templates/agent/consolidator_archive.md | 整合器存档模板 |\n| dream_phase1.md | nanobot/templates/agent/dream_phase1.md | 梦想阶段1模板 |\n| dream_phase2.md | nanobot/templates/agent/dream_phase2.md | 梦想阶段2模板 |\n| evaluator.md | nanobot/templates/agent/evaluator.md | 评估器模板 |\n| max_iterations_message.md | nanobot/templates/agent/max_iterations_message.md | 最大迭代消息模板 |\n| subagent_announce.md | nanobot/templates/agent/subagent_announce.md | 子代理公告模板 |\n| subagent_system.md | nanobot/templates/agent/subagent_system.md | 子代理系统模板 |\n| untrusted_content.md | nanobot/templates/agent/_snippets/untrusted_content.md | 不可信内容处理指南 |"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "heading_3",
      "heading_3": {
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "2.3 内存和心跳模板"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "code",
      "code": {
        "language": "markdown",
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "| 文件名 | 路径 | 作用 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| MEMORY.md | nanobot/templates/memory/MEMORY.md | 长期记忆模板 |\n| HEARTBEAT.md | nanobot/templates/HEARTBEAT.md | 心跳任务模板 |"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "heading_2",
      "heading_2": {
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "3. 硬编码的提示词"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "heading_3",
      "heading_3": {
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "3.1 核心系统硬编码提示词"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "code",
      "code": {
        "language": "markdown",
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "| 位置 | 提示词内容 | 作用 |\n|------|-----------|------|\n| ContextBuilder._RUNTIME_CONTEXT_TAG | [Runtime Context — metadata only, not instructions] | 运行时上下文标签 |\n| ContextBuilder._build_runtime_context | 构建包含当前时间、通道和聊天ID的运行时上下文 | 提供运行时元数据 |"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "heading_3",
      "heading_3": {
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "3.2 工具相关硬编码提示词"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "code",
      "code": {
        "language": "markdown",
        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "| 工具 | 提示词内容 | 作用 |\n|------|-----------|------|\n| CronTool | Tool to schedule reminders and recurring tasks. | cron 工具描述 |\n| CronTool 参数说明 | 详细的参数说明和示例 | 指导用户如何使用 cron 工具 |"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
